Anne Weale ( b. June 20 in England ) was a popular British writer of 88 romance novels in Mills & Boon from 1955 to 2002 . She is writing an autobiography called " 88 Heroes…1 Mr Right " . Anne Weale born on June 20 in England . After selling short stories to a woman 's magazine while still at school , she became a newspaper reporter . Anne publised her first romance novel in 1955 and her last novel in 2002 . She wrote from 1998 to 2004 a website review column , Bookworm on the Net , for The Bookseller , the UK 's leading book trade press magazine . In May 2005 , she started a book - blog . Anne lives traveling by Europe and she is writing an autobiography called " 88 Heroes…1 Mr Right " . 